This file gives a short overview of the steps necessary to create b-tagging efficiency maps and apply b-tagging efficiency scale factors

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
1) Instructions for producing b-tagging efficiency maps:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

A) Enter the Analysis/EDSHyFT/test/ directory
B) Follow the instructions in the README.txt file in that directory to create b-tagging efficiency maps

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
2) Instructions for applying b-tagging efficiency scale factors
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

A) Enter the BTagSFTool/MiniAnalyzer/test/ directory
B) Follow the instructions in the README.txt file in that directory to apply b-tagging efficiency scale factors

